---
import "../styles/colors.css";
---

<style>
.rules-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 2rem auto 1.5rem;
  padding: 0 0.75rem;
  transform: translateX(-14%);
}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.rules-wrapper {
		transform: translateX(-9px);
		}
	}

.rules-shadow {
  position: absolute;
  top: -8px; /* extend shadow above */
  left: -1px; /* extend shadow left */
  width: calc(100% + 1px); /* full width with shadow on sides */
  height: calc(100% + 18px); /* full height with shadow top and bottom */
  background: var(--color-shadow);
  border-radius: 1rem;
  z-index: 0;
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* outline all sides */
}

.rules-container {
  position: relative;
  padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
  background-color: var(--color-bg);
  border-radius: 1rem;
  font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
  z-index: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.rules-heading {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--color-text);
}

.rules-section ul {
  padding-left: 1rem;
  list-style: disc;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.rules-note {
  margin-top: 0.25rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--color-text-light);
}
</style>

<!-- RULES SECTION -->
<section class="rules-wrapper">
  <div class="rules-shadow"></div>
  <div class="rules-container">
    <div class="rules-section">
      <h2 class="rules-heading">I WON’T DRAW…</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>NSFW art that includes another person’s character without their consent</li>
        <li>Bestiality</li>
        <li>Incest</li>
        <li>NSFW of minors</li>
        <li>Gore</li>
        <li>Acts of self-harm</li>
        <li>Real people</li>
        <li>Race-bending</li>
        <li>Any hateful, offensive, or discriminatory content</li>
        <li>Fetishes including (but not limited to): fart, piss, scat, inflation, food, pregnancy</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="rules-note">[Feel free to ask if you're unsure about a specific fetish]</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rules-section">
      <h2 class="rules-heading">I WILL DRAW…</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Additional fees:</strong>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
            <li>Ornate outfits</li>
            <li>More than two limbs</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>May have fees depending on complexity:</strong>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
            <li>Machines / Robots</li>
            <li>Aliens</li>
            <li>Furries</li>
            <li>Body hair</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Fictional characters</li>
        <li>Humans</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="rules-note">[Feel free to ask if you think a character doesn’t fit any of the criteria listed above!]</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rules-section">
      <h2 class="rules-heading">Add-ons :3</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Priority:</strong> +50%
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
            <li>Skip the line or provide a deadline</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Complex Backgrounds:</strong> +75%
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
            <li>The background is flat or patterned by default</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="rules-section">
      <h2 class="rules-heading">Notes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>I currently only accept illustration commissions! I'm thinking of opening animation loop commissions, I'll do that when I'm ready :o)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
